Class ApprenticeshipLearningRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.singleagent.learnfromdemo.IRLRequest
      • burlap.behavior.singleagent.learnfromdemo.apprenticeship.ApprenticeshipLearningRequest

  • public class ApprenticeshipLearningRequest
extends IRLRequest
    A data structure for setting all the parameters of Max Margin Apprenticeship learning.
    Author:
    Stephen Brawner and Mark Ho
